Interpreting the model output as the probability that target words have the same meaning in both of the sentences, we predict True if the output turns 2Source code, experiments, requirements and results can be found at https://github.com/zhestyatsky/ MCL-WiCout to be greater than 0.5 or we predict False other- wise.
